{"tid":1879494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post］情人節晚做咩好？","createTime":"2020-02-14T08:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T08:50:36.000Z","uid":270270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3393c413a7986023d56cc8dc7b81fae3cb7026d4","tid":1879494,"uid":270270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5AWN70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5AWN70.jpg&h=a2506843&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見連登無post，怕大家唔知所以膽粗粗出post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">雖然疫情令大家都少左出街 日子唔好過<br />\n但收押所入面嘅手足又何嘗好過...<br />\n大家仲記唔記得上次見到手足回應嘅溫暖感覺？<br />\n我地一齊為手足送上情人節嘅小小支持好無？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">無論你係有情人又好 毒毒子如我也好<br />\n今晚抽到時間嘅 可以一齊去同手足隔窗一聚嘛？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">P牌仔推唔郁😖有勞各位Ching 幫手了</span>"},{"pid":"b4277001ab15c9e9e85fbae5ca46a9b1019db2b8","tid":1879494,"uid":80215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"425e3ed0ddbdf4294049cfa4ce697c964bd1e257","tid":1879494,"uid":80215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"49a2e27b2278409e300cca574692948da69fe3ba","tid":1879494,"uid":80215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8d18b18b07f14615c8067400ec8e6c6eef1dfc44","tid":1879494,"uid":80215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf20275412cd92b23b31b6908791ddab62e66344","tid":1879494,"uid":80215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"be4297c18eecda0b071de5ccf8ab89d5bad8befc","tid":1879494,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum